\cf0 I do think that I felt real moments of neglect, and I probably have downplayed this. I truly resented people like Takmina and Jacob, Ulan and others where I felt threatened and really jealous of how much my parents cared for them. I don\'92t recall the neglect specifically, but the fact that those relationships evoked such a strong reaction from me, even well into my adulthood, has to be a sign that those feeling came from a real place of feeling like I didn\'92t have enough attention, like I wasn\'92t important enough.\
