\cf0 Add in the very strong feelings of wanting to move back to the states in the formative years. I think I have tended to put a bow on some of those feelings as I\'92ve gotten older, shrugging it off by saying that I gained lots of cool experiences, which is true. But I still need to acknowledge that I paid a real price for my parents decision to live a missionary lifestyle.\
